for raid newbies   ask about these general raid to do things if you have any questions<br>
<br>
/seversidefilter on   <br>
     keeps all the extra info from adding to lag<br>
     with this off  then the auctions that you have turned off  <br>
     still add to lag  but dont add to spam<br>
    <br>
/auction off unless that's the raid channel<br>
/guild off  unless its a guild raid<br>
/showspelleffects off<br>
     saves bunches on lag<br>
/assist Kitaqua  (or whomever the MA )<br>
/g assisting  Kitaqua on  << %t >><br>
learn /assist <br>
know /assist <br>
use /assist<br>
let your group know you are using it  (optional)<br>
but i like it if i missed original call<br>
also lets group leader be the one to tell you dont start yet<br>
vs making the raid leader do it.<br>
